================================================================================
Protocols and technical foundation
================================================================================

NekoFlash implements the ADB and Fastboot wire protocols and AVB/vbmeta image
parsing based on the public specifications of the Android Open Source Project
(AOSP), licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0.

    Android Open Source Project
    Copyright (C) The Android Open Source Project
    https://source.android.com
    Licensed under the Apache License, Version 2.0

The protocol implementations in NekoFlash are independent original work written
in Kotlin on top of the Android USB Host API (UsbManager / UsbDeviceConnection).
No source code from AOSP is copied into this product.

