The following open-source projects inspired ideas and approaches in NekoFlash.
No source code from these projects is included; only concepts were studied.

  * termux-adb / termux-api (https://github.com/nohajc/termux-adb)
      Inspiration for operating ADB/USB from Android without root.

  * MiTool by offici5l (https://github.com/offici5l/MiTool)
